        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item bg-none border-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-check-square align-middle me-2"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path></svg>
          Flip 自动买入和按需挂单， 实现flip 自动化
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>